This repository has substantial portions derived from code shared by the ContextLab https://github.com/ContextLab/sherlock-topic-model-paper/. The copyright associated with this is shown below. 

For the sherlock_helpers files: only minor modifications are made to the ContextLab code. The modified lines are marked with a comment or block comment.

Otherwise, the modifications are fairly extensive. This includes changing the hyperparameters for the topic model, among several other changes.

